902 \u0915\u094b\u0930\u094b\u0928\u093e \u0935\u093e\u092f\u0930\u0938 \u0915\u0947 126 \u0938\u0948\u0902\u092a\u0932 \u0915\u0940 \u091c\u093e\u0902\u091a \u0930\u093f\u092a\u094b\u0930\u094d\u091f \u0928\u0947\u0917\u0947\u091f\u093f\u0935|website=Dainik Jagran|language=hi|access-date=8 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ANI/status/1248218082482454529|title=At present, 21 #COVID19 positive cases are in isolation wards. It's sad that all these cases are linked with Jamaat, some of them are those who had attended the Markaz event in Delhi & others are those who had come in contact with the attendees: Himachal Pradesh CM Jairam Thakurpic.twitter.com/xRYJC7uvXK|last=ANI|date=9 April 2020|website=@ANI|language=en|access-date=9 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Jammu and Kashmir]]\n|22\n|2\n|<ref name=\"ToI400Linkage2Apr\" />\n|-\n|[[Jharkhand]]\n|{{ndash}}\n|{{ndash}}\n|<ref name=\"ET647Cases3April\">{{cite news|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/647-positive-cases-from-14-states-in-last-two-days-are-linked-to-tablighi-jamaat-health-ministry/articleshow/74967407.cms|title=647 coronavirus positive cases from 14 states in last two days are linked to Tablighi Jamaat: Health Ministry|date=3 April 2020|work=The Economic Times|access-date=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Karnataka|Karnataka]]\n|50\n|1\n|<ref name=\"DainikJagranSpike3Apr\" /><ref name=\"karunadu4apr2\">{{cite web|url=https://karunadu.karnataka.gov.in/hfw/kannada/nCovDocs/04-04-2020(English).pdf|title=Media Bulletin|last=|first=|date=|website=Drpartment of health and family welfare services,Karnataka|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404141415/https://karunadu.karnataka.gov.in/hfw/kannada/nCovDocs/04-04-2020%28English%29.pdf|archive-date=4 April 2020|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ANI/status/1248216465792053250|title=16 more #COVID19 cases reported in Karnataka in the las